quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  41,39,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko tindinЙ—i e mawngu e gootaagu e kattal Makko wuurnitugol, tawde a yi'ay leydi ndin no yoori, ndi alaa puЙ—i. Si wonii non Men jippinii ndiyam toЙ“o e mayri, ndi dillira aawdi mariindi e mayri ndin, ndi fontoo. Awa wuurnituЙ—o ndii leydi On puЙ—i, pellet, ko wuurnitoowo maayЙ“e Й“en, fii Гұaaweede yoЙ“ee, tawde pellet, ko O hattanЙ—o kala huunde. Wuurnitugol leydi yoorunoondi ronkintaa Mo, wanaa fii wuurnitugol maayЙ“e e genaale mun."
  41,40,"Pellet, ooГұotooЙ“e Й“en e Aayeeje Amen Alla Й—en, Й“e yedda Й—e Й“e fenna, Й“e wayla Й—e, fii maЙ“Й“e suuЙ—aaki Men; MeЙ—en anndi fii maЙ“Й“e. E ko feroyteeЙ—o on ka Yiite Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kaa ko aroyoowo on Г‘alnde Darngal himo hoolii daЙ—ugol lepte? Onon Й“ee yiimЙ“e, huuwee ko yiЙ—uЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere maa bone, Men Й“annginanii on Й—ate moЖҙЖҙere e bone Й—en fow. Ko pellet, Allah no reeni ko golloton e Й—in kon. Hunnde e kuuЙ—e mon, suuЙ—aaki Mo."
  41,41,"YeddunooЙ“e Й“en Alqur'aana tuma nde arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, immorde e Allah, ko leptoyteeЙ“e Г‘alnde Darngal, feere mun alaa. Pellet non, ko nde Deftere teddunde foolunde. Gooto hattanaa waylude nden, maa wattita nde."
  41,42,"Meere iwrantaa nde yeeso mayre, wanaa Й“aawo mayre; foti koi Й—uytugol maa Й“eydugol, waylugol maa wattitugol. Ko nde jipporiinde immorde ka Г‘eeГұo e tagu Mun, e eЙ“Й“oore Mun e sari'a Mun On, YettiniiЙ—o e kala fiyaaku On."
  41,43,"A wi'aaka an NulaaЙ—o, immorde e fenneede, si wanaa ko NulaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e ma Й“en wi'anoo. MuГұГұo, sabu pellet, Joomi maa, ko O Jom yaafuyee kala tuubanЙ—o Mo e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e Jom lepte muusuЙ—e e kala haЙ“Й“itiiЙ—o e junuubi, o ronki tuubude."
  41,44,"Si Men waЙ—uno ndee Alqur'aanaare e haala goo, hara wanaa aarabu, heeferЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'ayno: ko haЙ—no Aayeeje mayre Й—en Й“annginiree, no men faamira? Alqur'aana wonay e haala ajami, arduЙ—o e mayre on wona aarabuujo? An NulaaЙ—o, maakan Й“ee: Alqur'aana, wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah Й“en Й“e goongini NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, ko fewnaynde itta e majjere, e sellinaynde Гұabbuuli majjere Й—in ka Й“ernde e ko jokki Й—um. ЖҒe gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en kan Allah, pahu no e noppi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, kayre hinde niЙ“Й“itani Й“e, Й“e faamataa nde. ЖҒen siforiiЙ“e Й—in sifaaji, hino wa'i wa noddirteeЙ“e e nokku woЙ—Й—uЙ—o, ko honno Й“e nanirta ndun noddaandu?"
  41,45,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Tawreetaare nden, kono luutondira e mayre: woЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e gomЙ—ini nde, woЙ—Й“e Й“en yeddi nde. Si wanaa fii fodoore Allah nden, wonnde ko Г‘alnde Darngal O Гұaawoyta hakkunde jeyaaЙ“e Й“en, e ko Й“e luutondiri e mun kon, O Гұaawayno hakkunde luutondirnooЙ“e e fii Tawreeta Й“en; O feГұГұina goonguЙ—o on e meerenteejo on, O teddina goonguЙ—o On, O hoyna meereejo on. HeeferЙ“e Й“en kan, pellet, hiЙ“e e sikke sikkitiiЙ—o ndee Alqur'aanaare."
  41,46,"Kala golluЙ—o ko moЖҙЖҙi, ko kanko nafitorta Й—um, wanaa Allah nafitorta golle moЖҙЖҙe hay gooto. Kala kadi huuwuЙ—o ko boni, lorra mun ko e makko yantata, wanaa Allah woni ko bone geddi gooto e tagu Makko ngun, lorrata. O yoЙ“oyay kala e ko hanndi kon. Joomi maa an NulaaЙ—o, O siforaali wonnde, tooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. O Й—uytanoytaaЙ“e moЖҙЖҙi maЙ“Й“e, O Й“eydanoytaaЙ“e kadi bonЙ—i."